Program: Omnibus
Title: The House of the People
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376jt7
Last Broadcast Date: 06 March 1990
'A colossal barracks in a sea of mud'. Exploring the 'House of the People' in Bucharest and evaluating the cost in lives and historic buildings of the world's second-largest building, the Palace of Parliament.